                        <interp inst="t18760131-name-201" type="given" value="LUCY"></interp>LUCY CHANNON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi>) The signatures to these two letters are not in Soisson's writing, nor is the endorsement to this cheque.</p>
