                  <hi rend="italic">By</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. COLLINS</hi>. I suppose this agreement is in Soisson's writing as it is on this paper—I saw him write it but I did not see it before—the signatures to these two letters are alike and they are not signed by Ahlborn.</p>
